{"tid":638913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸後生既都要夜訓","createTime":"2018-04-23T06:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T07:18:21.000Z","uid":143481,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cab86a7acdc7597381e7de7d0a0e2bf587494022","tid":638913,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"當你平均十一點訓<br />\n姐係出街既話最遲要十點番到屋<br />\n食完個飯都九點啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁後生去玩啦屌<br />\n到左三四十歲忙撚到你日日都早訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你覺得自己唔係毒撚又日日早訓既解釋黎聽下<br />\n<br />\n利申講緊既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後生仔</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9b65142f8b5de5f7ce804efa97f23940b1f3069","tid":638913,"uid":143481,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"到你死撚左就真係日日訓啦<br />\n後生唔夜訓等幾時<br />\n你甘心你成世就係咁撚規律咩！！<br />\n醒呀毒撚們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afa1791ad66e38f3bb4573075adb9bed4ffeab3","tid":638913,"uid":27210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔俾你早瞓<br />\n但唔好日日囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4015e00064de418abad31de3a5b404a84f607e0c","tid":638913,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ad175b491d6341bbcd3a381d3e0335e3498fb14","tid":638913,"uid":143481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6afa1791ad66e38f3bb4573075adb9bed4ffeab3","tid":638913,"uid":27210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔俾你早瞓<br />\n但唔好日日囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"咁夜訓都唔好日日既<br />\n有時精神真係要緊<br />\n但你日日早訓既話我肯撚定你係毒撚黎<img src=\"/assets/fac